description:
One day, a 28-year-old company employee suddenly dies. Being made to reincarnate to a certain planet by a mysterious young man, this is a tale of how he conveniently uses his overflowing abilities to go on a simple journey. Although he is the strongest protagonist, he does not realize his strength.

This is not a story where a cute girl comes out. There is no harem. There is not a single element of romance.

This is the life in another world of a young man who, along with his unique comrade, continued on a journey while collecting raw materials. And so~ometimes fights.>
